videos.description: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander forces a steal and then races to the hoop for the transition slam.
videos.headline: Gilgeous-Alexander electrifies UK with steal and slam

videos.description: Georgia's Tyree Crump dribbles behind the arc and shoots in rhythm for the deep triple.
videos.headline: Crump drains 3 from NBA range

videos.description: Kentucky's Wenyen Gabriel drains a 3-pointer at the top of the key to take a 10-point lead against Georgia.
videos.headline: Gabriel good from deep

videos.description: Kentucky's Shai Gilgeous-Alexander maintains concentration through contact to get the and-1 bucket.
videos.headline: Gilgeous-Alexander goes strong in paint for and-1

videos.description: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander gets the rebound and passes it to Quade Green who goes right to PJ Washington for the two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Everyone gets a touch on Kentucky fast break
